divs: Sighting DetailsI and 5 other people were on lake Murray in a boat and I saw the beautiful stars and decided to take a pic of them. I aimed the camera up at the stars and snapped the pic hoping that it would take. I got a pic of this thing in the sky. To me it looks odd. I immediately showed my husband and then he looked up also. Did not see anything. I showed my friends on the boat as well. They looked up and saw nothing. What is this?
trends: There have been no other sightings in Santee
This sighting has never been favorited.
